@namespace DaisyBlazor.Theming

@* Theme provider (MudThemeProvider-compatible). Applies the daisyUI data-theme
   attribute on the document element via IJSRuntime, resolves "system" via
   prefers-color-scheme, and persists the preference to localStorage + cookies.
   Cascades itself so descendants can read the current preference / dark-mode
   state and call SetThemeAsync. The light/dark theme names and the selectable
   theme list are parameter-driven, so any app can supply its own daisyUI themes. *@

<CascadingValue Value="this">
    @ChildContent
</CascadingValue>
